<%- include('partials/head') %>
<div class="ballot-head"><div class="bar"></div><div class="hairlines"></div></div>
<p class="eyebrow">Ballot received</p>
<h1>Your ballot was cast</h1>
<p>Your ballot in <strong><%= election.title %></strong> was sealed and stored. Your credential is now spent and cannot be used again.</p>
<div class="stat-row">
  <div class="stat"><div class="n"><%= turnout %></div><div class="l">Ballots cast so far</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="n"><%= eligible %></div><div class="l">Eligible voters</div></div>
</div>
<div class="notice seal">
  For your protection, this page does not repeat your selections — a screen that echoes choices
  can be used to pressure members into proving how they voted. Your ballot is encrypted and
  unlinkable to you. For ballot secrecy, also delete the email that carried your credential.
</div>
<a class="btn" href="/">Done</a>
<%- include('partials/foot') %>
